			<p>Choose the Covenant of Blood, the Covenant of Disaster, the Covenant of Flame, the Covenant of Frost, the Covenant of Instinct, the Covenant of Plague, or the Covenant of Shadow, each detailed at the end of the class description. Your choice grants you features at 2nd level and again at 7th, and 15th level.</p>
		</description>
